    <comment>Re-add packetdrill to Factory (was removed). Update to 2.0+git.20260514 (PSP support, AccECN, tcp_info sync to v6.16). Rebase the SUSE Makefile patch. Build with -fno-strict-aliasing (checksum code type-puns the packet buffer; -O2 strict aliasing miscompiled it, failing checksum_test) and use the distro %optflags as-is. Builds green on all enabled arches incl. s390x/ppc64le.</comment>
